text: Brenda Joy Kaplan (born October 14, 1966), known by her stage name Brenda K. Starr, is an American singer and songwriter. She is well known originally in R&B;, dance and pop but now mostly in salsa-based music. She is also well known for her 1980s work with freestyle music.
